headline: Wynn Resorts, Limited (WYNN) Drops Bid for New York City Casino License
summary: Wynn Resorts, Limited (NASDAQ:WYNN) has decided to withdraw its bid for a casino license in New York. The company, a publicly traded hospitality and gaming firm based in Paradise, Nevada, announced that the ongoing rezoning process revealed more effective ways to allocate its capital.
